<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[ل]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[أَبْطَلَ]</span> الرجلُ: إِذا جاء بالباطل،<span class="c5"> قال اللّاه تعالى:</span> وَخَسِرَ هُناالِكَ الْمُبْطِلُونَ <span class="c2">«١»</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وأَبْطَلْتُ الشيءَ فبَطَلَ،<span class="c5"> قال اللّاه تعالى:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَيُبْطِلَ الْبااطِلَ <span class="c2">«٢»</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[ن]</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[أبْطَنَ]</span>: خلاف أَظْهَرَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">ويقال:</span> أَبْطَنْتُ فلاناً دون فلان: أي جعلتُه أَخصَّ منه.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">وأَبْطَنْتُ البعير:</span> إِذا شددته بالبِطان.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[همزة]</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c4">[أَبْطَأَ]</span> مهموز: نقيض أَسْرَعَ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
